               <p>Second Count for stealing the said lead against the statute, <rs id="t17730626-48-cd279" type="crimeDate">May 24</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730626-48-off275 t17730626-48-cd279"></join>. *</p>
               <p>James Green. On this day week the prisoners were at work for me, at Sir 
               <persName id="t17730626-48-person580">
                  Benj.
                   Trueman
               <interp inst="t17730626-48-person580" type="surname" value="Trueman"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730626-48-person580" type="given" value="Benj."></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730626-48-person580" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's, in <placeName id="t17730626-48-crimeloc280">Brick lane, Spitalfields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17730626-48-crimeloc280" type="placeName" value="Brick lane, Spitalfields"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17730626-48-crimeloc280" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730626-48-off275 t17730626-48-crimeloc280"></join>; about a quarter after eight in the morning, I was standing at Low's door in Pater-noster-row, in the same parish, and the prisoner came by; I suspected they had some lead about them, and desired Mr. Low to assist me to take them; we followed them a cross Bishopsgate-street into a coach yard; they went to the top of the yard, and stood pausing a while; then they turned back down another alley; I was afraid they would escape, so I laid hold of Brittle, and called to Mr. Low to assist in taking the other; we took them to Spitalfields watch-house. I desired Brittle to take the lead out, and he took it from under his waistcoat; that lead fitted the place the lead was taken from; it was taken from the gutter of the copper in the brewhouse; there is about 35 lb. of it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17730626-48-person581">
                  Robert
                   Low
               <interp inst="t17730626-48-person581" type="surname" value="Low"></interp>
